graph LR
    ODHModelController[ODH Model Controller]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ODHModelController -->|extends functionality| KServe[KServe v0.13+<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODHModelController -->|creates Routes| RouteAPI[OpenShift Route API v1<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODHModelController -->|processes templates| TemplateAPI[OpenShift Template API v1<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODHModelController -->|watches/creates resources| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    ODHModelController -.->|VirtualServices, Gateways, mTLS| Istio[Istio/Maistra Service Mesh v2.5+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODHModelController -.->|AuthConfig for auth| Authorino[Authorino v0.14+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODHModelController -.->|AuthPolicy for auth| Kuadrant[Kuadrant AuthPolicy v1beta3<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODHModelController -.->|ServiceMonitor/PodMonitor| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.68+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODHModelController -.->|TriggerAuthentication| KEDA[KEDA v2.14+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODHModelController -.->|webhook TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager v1.13+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODHModelController -.->|model catalog, pull secrets| NGC[NVIDIA NGC API<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ODHModelController -->|reads config| DSCInit[DSCInitialization<br/>ODH Internal]
    ODHModelController -->|reads enablement| DSC[DataScienceCluster<br/>ODH Internal]
    ODHModelController -.->|registers metadata| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>ODH Internal<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Integration Points (Components that use ODH Model Controller)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|UI management| ODHModelController
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto-deploy models| ODHModelController
    Notebooks[Jupyter Notebooks] -.->|deploy from notebooks| ODHModelController

    %% External Services (Runtime Dependencies)
    InferencePod[Inference Pods<br/>Created by KServe] -->|model artifacts| S3[S3 Storage<br/>Runtime]
    InferencePod -->|pull images| Registry[Container Registry<br/>Runtime]

    %% Conditional Features
    ODHModelController -.->|MESH_DISABLED=false| Istio
    ODHModelController -.->|MODELREGISTRY_STATE=replace| ModelRegistry
    ODHModelController -.->|NIM_STATE=replace| NGC

    %% Serving Runtimes (Supported)
    ODHModelController -->|deploys templates| vLLM[vLLM Runtimes<br/>CPU, CUDA, Gaudi, ROCm, Multinode]
    ODHModelController -->|deploys templates| Caikit[Caikit Standalone/TGIS]
    ODHModelController -->|deploys templates| OVMS[OpenVINO Model Server]
    ODHModelController -->|deploys templates| HF[HuggingFace Detector]

